When does a notifier does effect?

When your friends send to you a notifier it is deactivated as default. If you want to active a notifier touch right-top button and select \'active\'.
Also! If a notifier contains a special packet, that packet will be offer your approval before send.
Why there are my profile picture at the both side?

Because you are condition supervisor and you will be notified (or you will send message) when condition is right. There is profile picture of condition supervisor on the left side every time. On the right side, there are profile picture of will be notified or who will send message.
Why there are profile picture of my friend at the both side?

Because your friend is condition supervisor and him will be notified (or him will be send message) when condition right. There is profile picture of condition supervisor on the left side every time. On the right side, there are profile picture of will be notified or who will send message.

This meaning that notifier will be effect for as long as it is active. If you wish you can add time restrict to that notifier: touch top-right button and select \'edit\'. For example: at the 12/02/2018 range of 12:00 - 13:30.
What are meaning time and date indicators below the notifier?
This is meaning, that notifier will be effect (if it is active) at the %s and range of %s - %s.
What are meaning time indicators at the below the notifier?
This is meaning, that notifier will be effect (if it is active) at the range of %s - %s.
What is meaning date indicator at the below notifier?
This is meaning, that notifier will be effect (if it is active) at the specified date.
I want to close notifications for this notifier

It is too easy. Click right-top button of notifier that you want to close notifications for it and select \'Close notifications\' or you can touch to notification icon on the notifier to open/close notifications.
What do you want to share with your friends when? An profile updater consist of what your answer for this question.

Think about an alarm application. An alarm application want to you to answer this question: \"When and how do i wake you up?\". Opcon asks \"Whom shall I inform about the events whose mobile phone notifies ?\" That\'s all!

When does a notifier does effect?

An notifier that you send to your friends it is deactivated as default. It does not any effect until your friend active it. Also! If the notifier contains special packet, that special packets will send after approval your friends (Even if it is active).
